SummaryEnglish: Tang San is one of Tang Sect martial art clan's most prestigious disciples and peerless in the use of hidden weapons. With high expectations, the sect's elders believe his future will be bright; yet Tang chooses to forsake this life at the cost of obtaining the sect's forbidden lore—an action punishable by death. Tang, now content with his ascension of knowledge, sees no reason to keep on living and jumps from Hell's Peak, but little did he know that that would not be the end of his existence.

1.SummaryEnglish: Extended directors cut of combined episodes 261, 262 and 263.
The previous life of Tang Sect martial arts clan's Tang San ended and he's born again as Tang San into the other world known as Douluo Dalu.

2.SummaryEnglish: The day to awaken the martial soul has arrived. Tang San and the other children from the village attended. What would Tang San's martial soul?

3.SummaryEnglish: Tang San goes to Nuoding School to study.

4.SummaryEnglish: Tang San wants to become Da Shi's (Grand Master) disciple. Will Da Shi accept him?

5.SummaryEnglish: Tang San meets with his new roommate and also classmate, Xiaowu. And he starts to learn things from his teacher, Dashi (Grand Master).

6.SummaryEnglish: Dashi (Grand Master) takes Tang San to get his first sprit ring.

7.SummaryEnglish: Tang San successfully got his very first yellow (100 years) spirit ring, which is close to upper limit of first spirit ring 423 Years.

8.SummaryEnglish: Xiao Wu becomes the leader in their class with the help of Tang San.

9.SummaryEnglish: Tang San studies at Nuoding School. At the same time, he works as a blacksmith at the local shop. After a year, he returns to his home with Xiao Wu.

10.SummaryEnglish: When Tang San arrived home, he found that he's father is gone. He was sad because he's got no family left. Because of that, he requests Xiao Wu to be his little sister. She agrees to it at the end. The child life is over at this point. After 5 years later, Tang San and Xiao Wu arrived at Suotuo City.

11.SummaryEnglish: Tang San fights with a guy he and Xiao Wu saw at the hotel. Will Tang San beat him? Also the guy told them while going for Shilake (Shrek) academy entance exam if face problem they should provide name "Dai Mu Bai".

12.SummaryEnglish: Tang San and Xiao Wu face the entrance examination to attend a academy named Shilake (Shrek).

13.SummaryEnglish: Tang San, Xiao Wu, Ning Rong Rong, Zhu Zhu Qing take the entrance examination to attend Shilake (Shrek) academy.

14.SummaryEnglish: As the final entrance examination, Tang San, Xiao Wu, Ning Rong Rong and Zhu Zhu Qing must face one of the teachers named Zhao Wuji. What will go wrong during the fight? Will they make it?

15.SummaryEnglish: Tang San, Xiao Wu, Ning Rong Rong and Zhu Zhu Qing get to attend Skilake school. Unfortunately, some misfortune comes to Zhao Wuji. What would it be?

16.SummaryEnglish: While Tang San and Xiao Wu look around, they come across a guy with Phoenix martial soul.

17.SummaryEnglish: With the appearance of Dai Mubai, Tang San and Xiao Wu realised that it was just a misunderstanding with Ma Hong Jun. And then they all become friends. While they are at the school Seven Precious Coloured Glaze Sect keeps taps on Ning Rong Rong.

18.SummaryEnglish: On the first day of attending Skilake School, Ning Rong Rong faces Fu Lande (Flender), the headmaster of the school directly with arrogance. But finally she failed and became sad. While she's out for a while, Fu Lande (Flender) takes the rest to a place where they can practice their fighting skills.

19.SummaryEnglish: Tang San and Xiao Wu AKA 3-5 combination face the powerful opponents in the competitions. Can they beat them?

20.SummaryEnglish: When they came back to school, they discovered that Dai Mu Bai and Ning Rong Rong are talking. But not good. The conversation goes south. No matter how, everything is fine again in the end. The next day, Zhao Wuji takes them to find a spirit ring for Oscar (Ao Si Ka).

21.SummaryEnglish: When they stay in a place for the night, they come across a teacher from Cangku School. They had some fights. The next day, they all continue to search in the forest.

22.SummaryEnglish: Some time passed, they finally found one. But there was someone interrupted them. Who would that be?

23.SummaryEnglish: Tang San fights with Meng Yiran for Oscar's spirit ring. Will he beat her?

24.SummaryEnglish: During the time they search for spirit beast for Tang San, unexpected thing happened. What would that be?

25.SummaryEnglish: Tang San follows the trace and tries to save Xiao Wu but unfortunately, he meets with Meng Yiran's grandfather and grandmother instead.

26.SummaryEnglish: Meng Yiran requests Tang San to compete her one more time. Tang San knows he can't avoid it but to agree. Will Tang San beat her again? Will Tang San can have his third spirit ring? What more will happen next?

51.SummaryEnglish: Tang San stays with Poison Douluo as his prisoner for six months. Meanwhile Tang San's friends are trying hard to get their skills improved.

52.SummaryEnglish: Poison Duoluo let Tang San go and Tang San is back to Shilake School.

53.SummaryEnglish: Tang San gives presents to his friends and his teacher, Dashi (Grand Master). Because of those presents, everyone except Xiao Wu, their skills improved a lot.

54.SummaryEnglish: Zhao Wuji tests Tang San and the rest of six kids. After the test finished, Tang San manages to detox Poison Duoluo's granddaughter.

55.SummaryEnglish: Tai Long challenges Tang San. Tang San has no choice but to accept. After that, Tang San and Xiao Wu look around the city.

56.SummaryEnglish: Tang San and Xiao Wu went to an auction and found out something awful. Meanwhile Tai Long's father comes to the school to get Tang San pay for what he did to his son.

57.SummaryEnglish: Tang San deals with Tai Long's father. Meanwhile Ning Rong Rong went back home.

58.SummaryEnglish: Tai Long's grandfather comes to school and challenges Tang San. Meanwhile, Ning Rong Rong demonstrates to her father what Tang San's hidden weapons can do.

59.SummaryEnglish: Tang San meets with some people who know about his father and learns something about his life. During their meeting with Ning Rong Rong's father Ning Feng Zhi, he wants Tang San to do some hidden weapons for their Sect.

60.SummaryEnglish: Tang San learns from his teacher, Dashi (Grand Master) about a truth of what his father did. Meanwhile, Ning Rong Rong realises her love for Oscar, but stops herself for saying anything because of her sect's rule.

67.SummaryEnglish: Tang San tells what his 4th spirit ring can do. After that Dashi (Grand Master) tells some important facts about upcoming big competition.

68.SummaryEnglish: Shilake School group arrived at the Tianduo Country's capital city. And then the competition begins.

69.SummaryEnglish: Shilake School Vs. Tianduo Royal Family School. Who will win?

70.SummaryEnglish: Tang San meets with crowned prince and gets to know more about what happened to his father.

71.SummaryEnglish: Because of the reason that Shilake School group's next opponent is very strong, Da Shi wants them to give up the competition. What would be their choice? They will choose to fight or they will just simply give up?

72.SummaryEnglish: Shilake School Vs. Xiang Jia School begins. How will Tang San guide his team to win?

73.SummaryEnglish: Ning Rongrong is so surprised to see how Tang San is genius. What did he do to make her that surprised?

74.SummaryEnglish: A teacher from Cangkui School wants to kill Tang San by trapping him in the fragmentary illusion dreamland. Can Tang San get out of it?

75.SummaryEnglish: Tang San got soul bone from that teacher, Shinian. Then Tang San shows Dashi (Grand Master) that soul bone. But due to it's not compatible with him, he couldn't take it. And then Dashi tells Tang San to forget all about it. After a few hours, the next competition begins.

76.SummaryEnglish: The match continues. The opponent that Shilake is facing in the current tournament is very strong. So, Tang San has to do everything he can. Would he win? Meanwhile, the students from Cangkui school is searching for their missing teacher.

77.SummaryEnglish: Shilake Vs. Cangkui. How would Tang San try to win the match and what kind of troubles he has to face afterwards?

78.TitleEnglish: Episode 078: Investigation of Shrek vs Blue Sunshine
78.SummaryEnglish: Tang San faces the interrogation where he can't tell the truth of what actually happened between them and Cangkui School. How could he get out of that interrogation?

79.TitleEnglish: Episode 079: Shrek vs Skywater Academy starts
79.SummaryEnglish: Shilake Vs. Tianshui (Sky Water) Academy match begins. How would Shilake try to win them?

80.SummaryEnglish: The match between Shilake and Tianshui isn't finished yet. Tang San is still trying to win. What would the result be? Meanwhile Poison Duoluo is facing with his one of the enemies.

81.SummaryEnglish: Poison Duoluo faces one of his enemies who is stronger than him. How would he try to win him? Meanwhile, Tang San is having some doubts with his plant martial soul. How would he overcome it?

82.SummaryEnglish: Shilake 7 students swaps pointers with Liu Erlong. Who would win? And then later, they all meet with crown prince Xue Qinghe.

83.SummaryEnglish: The next match begins. This time, they have to face Balake School which is very ignorant. Because of the changes of rules, they have to go on 1 Vs. 1 match. On Shilake School side, Xiao Wu comes out to fight. How she will try to win?

84.SummaryEnglish: Xiao Wu wins every fight she takes. But in order to hide the actual strength of Shilake, Dashi (Grand Master) decided to let Tang San to take the next fights. In the next fight, Tang San has to face Huo Wushuang. How would Tang San try to win?

85.SummaryEnglish: ang San wins 6 matches in a row. Finally, he has to face 1 Vs 1 match with Huo Wu. In order to win over Tang San, Huo Wu has to use up everything she has even her own life. Will Tang San win or lose that match?

86.SummaryEnglish: This time, Shilake has to face Zhiwu (Botanical) School. Unfortunately, because of the plan, they have to lose 3 or 4 matches. Finally, Ma Hongjun comes up next. He wins 5 matches in a row. As for the 6th match, it's kind of troublesome. Will he win?

87.SummaryEnglish: Huo Wu kisses Tang San on the cheek and Feng Xiaotian sees it. Later, Xiao Wu also kisses Tang San. They had beautiful moment. And then later, Shilake School faces Thunder School.

88.SummaryEnglish: In one match, because the opponent is too strong, Xiao Wu lost and wounded. So, Tang San asks Dai Mubai to take revenge for Xiao Wu. And Dai Mubai could take revenge for her. Later, Feng Xiaotian asks Tang San for one final match and Tang San agrees. The next day, the match between Feng Xiaotian and Tang San begins.

89.SummaryEnglish: Tang San Vs. Feng Xiaotian match begins. In order to win Feng Xiaotian, Tang San has to use the secret weapon which he's been hiding all those years. What would that weapon be and how would he try to win the match?

90.SummaryEnglish: Shilake School's students and the others face ambush on the way to Soul City.

91.SummaryEnglish: Those ones who are trying to kill students and teachers from Shilake School are very strong, so, Shilake's people are trying very hard to not to get killed. While Shilake's people are protecting themselves, a Fenghao (Titled) Douluo has arrived and find out some facts. Meanwhile, Dashi (Grand Master) goes to Wu Hun Dian (Spirit Hall Palace) to find an old friend to ask something.

92.SummaryEnglish: While Dashi (Grand Master) is asking the leader of Soul Palace, Bi Bi Dong about how to deal with double martial soul problem in Soul Palace, Shilake 7 students and teachers are facing Feng Hao (Titled) Duo Luo Ju Hua Guan. Fortunately, there are some people who like to help them. Who would that be?

93.SummaryEnglish: Even Poison Douluo is on Tang San and Shilake School's side, when another Douluo appeared on the enemy's side, he can't do that much. But situation's changed due to the other Duoluo appeared on Shilake School's side. Who is that Douluo and how would he try to save the situation?

94.SummaryEnglish: With the help from Ning Fengzhi and Sword Douluo, Tang San and Shilake school survive the ambush of Wu Hun Dian (Spirit Hall Palace). But unfortunately, Ning Rongrong's identity is revealed to Chihuo and Shenfeng Schools. They now know that Shilake School has the Daughter of the leader of Qi Bao Liu Li (Seven Precious Coloured Glaze) Sect which is the third powerful sect on this Soul Land.

95.SummaryEnglish: Tang San and Shilake school team arrive at Soul City and meet with Dashi (Grand Master) who just got back from Soul Palace. Then they prepare for the competition rounds. Meanwhile, Xiao Wu reaches level 40 and got a 4th soul loop.

96.SummaryEnglish: Shilake school team find out Shenfeng school and Chihuo school combined and make a new team called the new Shenfeng. In their first match, Shilake school team see their new strength. The next day, Shilake school team find out their very first match in Soul City is with Xingluo country's loyal family school team.

97.SummaryEnglish: Shilake school team and Xingluo country's royal family school team match begins. How would Shilake try to win?

98.SummaryEnglish: The match between Xingluo country's royal family school and Shilake school continue. The match is just a match for the others, but for Dai Mubai and Zhu Zhuqing, this match is life and death match. What kind of hatred makes them to be like that and how would Shilake school try to win the match?

99.SummaryEnglish: Tang San discovers Dai Mubai's real identity. And the next day, Tiaodou Royal Family School Vs. Soul Palace School match begins.

100.SummaryEnglish: Tiandou Royal Family School Vs. Wun Huan Dian (Soul Palace) School match begins. Who would win the match? And then later, they found out the champion prize for the school who wins the competition.

101.SummaryEnglish: Shilake Vs. New Shenfeng (Wind God) Academy match begins. This time, both sides use an extremely amazing technique. What would that be and who would be the winner?

102.SummaryEnglish: Shilake Vs. New Shenfeng match continues. How would it turn out? After the match, Tang San and the rest of 6 students take rest and prepare for tomorrow's final competition with Wu Hun Dian (Soul Palace) school.

103.SummaryEnglish: The final match, Shilake School Vs. Soul Place School begins. How would the match go?

104.SummaryEnglish: The final match between Shilake School and Soul Palace School still continues. This final match is not like any previous matches, so, Shilake's seven students have to use up all they have got. And as for Tang San, because of Xie Yue and Hu Liena's combined technique, he also has to use everything he's got. How would they try to win?

105.SummaryEnglish: The match between Shilake school and Soul Palace school still continues. In order to win the match, Tang San has to do everything he could. How would he try to win the match?

106.SummaryEnglish: Xiao Wu's the real identity is revealed and she has to face a lot of people from Soul Palace including Bi Bi Dong who want to kill her to take her soul loop and soul bone.

107.SummaryEnglish: Shilake School teachers and students against Soul Palace just to protect Xiao Wu. At the same time, Xiao Wu saw something belongs to her mother in Bi Bi Dong. Because people from Soul Palace are so strong, so, they can't match with them. But at nearly the end, someone appears. Who would that be?

108.SummaryEnglish: Tang San's father Tang Hao appears in front of Bi Bi Dong and takes Tang San and Xiao Wu. Dangerous event passed and so, Shilake students and teachers left Wuhun City and disbanded but the rest of 5 students (Dai Mubai, Oscar, Ma Hongjun, Zhu Zhuqing and Ning Rongrong) made a promise that they will come back to school and see each other after 5 years later.

109.SummaryEnglish: After Xiao Wu left, Tang Hao takes his son Tang San to some place to give him some practice. Meanwhile, Oscar went to Seven Precious Coloured Glaze Sect with Ning Rongrong and live there for some days.

110.SummaryEnglish: Tang Hao gives lessons to Tang San. Meanwhile, Ning Rongrong tells Oscar the reason why they can't be together.

115.SummaryEnglish: Hu Liena comes to Tang San to ask for a collaboration. In order to conceal the real identity from Hu Liena, Tang San says his name is Tang Yin. After a few days, both Hu Liena and Tang San complete 100th match and ask the King of Massacre City to open the Path of Hell.

116.SummaryEnglish: Hu Liena and Tang San (Tang Yin to Hu Liena) go on the Path of Hell.

117.SummaryEnglish: Tang San and Hu Liena deal together with the beast that lives in the lava thing of the Path of Hell.

125.SummaryEnglish: Tang San fights with 7th Elder, a Fenghao (Titled) Duoluo, Titled Lieyang (Fierce Yang), meanwhile Elder concil says Tang San fulfil 3 conditions to right the wrongs of the past.

126.SummaryEnglish: 5 of Shilake's 7 Monster (Dai Mubai, Tang San, Ma Hongjun, Ning Rongrong & Zhu Zhuqing) visit Shilake (Shrek) Acadmey as agreed 5 years ago, meanwhile Ao Sika (Oscar) is fighting for his Sixth Spirit ring.

127.SummaryEnglish: 5 of Shilake's 7 Monster (Dai Mubai, Tang San, Ma Hongjun, Ning Rongrong & Zhu Zhuqing) meet with Zhao Wuji, Qin Ming & Golden Iron Triangle (Flender, Yu Xiaogang, Liu Erlong) and share their last 5 years of experience, meanwhile Ao Sika (Oscar) is trying assimilate his 6th Spirit ring.

128.SummaryEnglish: Flender asks 5 of Shilake's 7 Monster to contribute school by arranging fight to motivate other students, their oppenent is arranged by Liu Erlong to be Zhao Wuju & Flender himself. Ao Sika (Oscar) expain his 6th Spirit ability to Hao Te, and he gives him back the newly obtained Spirit Bone to absorb.

129.SummaryEnglish: 5 of Shilake's 7 Monster fight with Flender & Zhai Quji. Spirit hall ready with plan and starts with Seven Treasure Glazed Tile Clan.

130.SummaryEnglish: Wu Hun Dian (Spirit Hall Palace) had commenced thier plan, Seven Treasure Glazed Tile Clan is invaded, Ning Feng Zhi comes to Shrek acedemy to info Grandmaster about attack and alert Blue Lightning Tyrant Dragon Clan, but it's too late. Tang San reaches Xingdou (Stardou) and anticpate his meet with Xiao Wu

131.SummaryEnglish: Tang San finds Spirit Hall members in XingDou (Star Dou) Forest, comes up plan to get in touch with them as Tang Yin resulting into conflict, Hu Liena joins them tries to mediate.

132.SummaryEnglish: Tang San successfully mingle with Spirit Hall people, to prevent capture of Xiao Wu. On the other hand Tian Dou empire's Emperor discusses with Da Shi (Grand Master) & Ning Fengzhi how to prevent Spirit Hall's domination & avenge their grievances.

133.SummaryEnglish: Spirit Hall people reach center of XingDou (Start Dou) Forest faces Er Ming & Xiao Wu and fight begans, later Da Ming also joins the fight against Ghost & Chrysanthemum Douluo. When rest people tries to catch Xiao Wu Tang intervenes & flee with Xiao Wu. Spirit Hall people pursing Tang San & Xiao Wu. When Tang San & Xiao Wu about to get away successfully, they are intercepted by Human faced spider of 30,000 years of cultivation & later caught up by Spirit Hall people.

134.SummaryEnglish: After being caught up by Spirit Hall remaining people; to save Xiao Wu, Tang San paralyzes her by hitting her acupoints and fights with them. As he realises, he won't be able to both of them, he plans to sacifice himself to let Xiao Wu go, he intentionally destorys this right to give his right leg sprit bone which has flying ability to Xiao Wu. While Xiao Wu sees Tang San being bombarded with attacks, she ignites 1,00,000 years spirit ability to sacrifice herself. As Tang San isn't strong enough to handle 1,00,000 years spirit ring, she also melds are soul with her ring to stabilise her spirit ring with Tang San. during which even though Tang San has lost his consciousness but his soul sees and tries but unable to stop Xiao Wu.

135.SummaryEnglish:
Tang San wakes up to find a Soft Bone Demon Rabbit near by comes to realise it's Xiao Wu long side Yearning Heartbroken Red (flower). He knows Yearning Heartbroken Red has life saving uses it on Rabbit (Xiao Wu). After waiting for 10 days Tang San realises Rabbit (Xiao Wu) isn't Recognising him. Er'Ming (Titan Giant Ape) tells Rabbit is just body of Xiao Wu and lost her 1,00,000 years of cultivation and soul as she had used extreme method of sacrifice to save him. Er'Ming after having discussion with Da'Ming (Azure Sky Bull Python) tells Tang San that to save Xiao Wu, he must fulfil 3 conditions, first of which is to collect 3 medicine plants.
1. 10,000 year old Sacred Soul Grass to awaken her soul
2. 10,000 year Ginseng King Grade 9 to reshape her human form
3. Neidan from Ancient Spirit Beast to unite her soul and body

136.SummaryEnglish: After absorping 30,000 years Man Faced Demon spider Tang San's  8 Lance spider exteranl spirit bone is not only evolved but forms unique condition where in his 4 spirit bone (50,000 years head bone, 8 Lance spider exteranl spirit bone, 100,000 years right arm bone, 100,000 years right leg bone) fuses and form external armor and comes into conflict with eachother, which he's unable to comprend decides to confirm it with his teacher, Da Shi (Grand Master). Coming to Tian Dou city he meets with Dugu Bo, Poison Douluo after coming in clash with 4th Prince Xue Beng. Dugu Bo tells him to consider other perspective, as things may not seem as they are.

137.SummaryEnglish: After having discussion with Dugu Bo, Tang San return to Shrek Academy to meet with his teacher. Tang San informs his teacher (Yu Xiaogang), teacher's wife (Liu Er'long) & Dean (Flender) of his happening. Realising his predicament Tang San find establishing "Tang Sect" as feasibile solution to fight againt Spirit Hall, he discusses it with Ma Hongjun and asks Ning Rongrong to invite Ning Fengzhi. while moving Tang San finds he's being tailed and comes up with guess by picking up couple things like other person's voice.

138.SummaryEnglish: Tang San and Ao Sika (Oscar) recognise eachother during the fight, after that they share their last 5 years experience with eachother. Tang San discuss with Grandmaster about armor he came across while upgrade of 8 Lance spider external spirit bone, to which Grandmaster identifies as Spirt Bone fusion. Tang San is about meet with Ning Feng Zhi, where Ao Sika (Oscar) and Ning Rongrong come face to face with eachother
